title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 9
description:
In this video we will look at the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace this week. This week multiple livery packs for F1 teams are released as several mission packs including ones to improve you landing skills at certain airports. Additionally some new airports have been released including 2 from ORBX.
